metadata.name: Stray cats of 2049 / 01
metadata.description:
Imagine a distopian world where the streets of Tokyo in 2049 are so tough and the conditions are so harsh that even the stray cats need new skills ... and devices to survive - which, for example, are added to the animals by crazy street samurai bio-hackers, or they are mutated ( bio/nanotech) ...
I made a limited series of these imaginary characters of street cats to be used as avatars

This is an experimentary project with midjourney app to create a series of characters. 

01/14  - Midjourney AI + A. Photoshop
